Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:14.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}To another fly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:24.52,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}制作：akira 安静の云
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要当护卫呢 麻烦死了
